#

Chilled Beet Soup (Holodnik)

15 min
$8
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

Cold SoupLight MealHealthy

Description

A refreshing and vibrant chilled soup made with beets, perfect for warm days.

Ingredients

  • beets, cooked and grated: 2 cups
  • cucumber, diced: 1
  • radishes, thinly sliced: 1/2 cup
  • green onions, chopped: 1/4 cup
  • plain yogurt or sour cream: 1 cup
  • vegetable broth: 2 cups
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh dill, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
